problem1 :  stdio.h not found
------------------------------
hello_world.c:1:11: fatal error: stdio.h: No such file or directory
 # include <stdio.h>
           ^~~~~~~~~
sol: 
find /usr/include/ -name "stdio.h"
sudo apt install --reinstall build-essential ^C

find /usr/include/ -name "stdio.h"
/usr/include/c++/7/tr1/stdio.h
/usr/include/x86_64-linux-gnu/bits/stdio.h
/usr/include/stdio.h

